item.title: Contributing to Git
item.description: Create your own branch in Github Write your feature Pull code from master/main branch and rebase git pull origin main --rebase Follow prompts in files mentioned in output

item.title: Updating Firmware
item.description: Plug RoboRio USB-B - USB-A cable into laptop Open Phoenix Tuner Open Control Install (default tab) Run Diagnostic Server Open CAN Devices tab Check firmware version against latest in ctre firmware folder The CTRE Firmware Folder can be downloaded from any CTRE product page If you can see devices follow the prompt in the bottom left, if not diagnose errors
